title: Episode 128: Tripp Advice - Going From Nothing To 1 Million Subscribers
description:
In this episode, Robbie interviews Tripp Advice aka Tripp Kramer, a dating coach and YouTube Influencer with almost a million followers. They discuss how Tripp moved to LA with no job and no experience with women, and what he did to overcome his shyness and date the women of his dreams while simultaneously creating a lucrative career in a field he was passionate about...

Show Notes:

How Tripp got started, battling approach anxiety in LA before Tinder and dating apps were even a thing... (03:00)

Should you go out to the bars sober to meet women if you're a beginner? (04:40)

A little known secret to rapid success that most guys fail to implement early enough in their journey... (05:10)

How to avoid the trap of becoming "Whipped Cream On Shit"... (06:20)

If you're not attracting the women you really want, do this... (08:50)

Do you feel comfortable interacting with women? If the answer is no, how to transform it... (11:00)

How to decide when to get into a relationship if you've been approaching and getting results... (12:30)

What you MUST do if you’re looking for a relationship... (14:50)

The "Super-Abundance" mentality how it can actually become counter productive... (16:00)

Everyone says to avoid the victim mentality and take radical ownership, but is it that easy?... (17:30)

The mindset you must adopt to protect yourself if your girlfriend cheats on you, breaks up with, or even dies… (18:45)

What could happen to your relationship if you feel like you got lucky... (20:00)

Is dating, pickup, and approaching women dangerous or addictive behavior?... (25:00)

How to avoid the trap of becoming a female validation seeking junky... (27:45)

How Tripp started a business from nothing and reached 1 Million YouTube subscribers... (30:00)

What happened when his first podcast and YouTube channel failed... (32:30)

What would be the difference between starting a business selling dating advice now versus in 2012?... (33:00)

Is there such thing as an overnight success?...(33:30)

An amazing analogy to keep your business alive and growing... (38:00)

The passive income and 4-hour-work-week myth... (39:00)

Can you still make money in the dating advice space? What will happen in this politically correct world? (40:00)

Links-

TrippAdvice.com

channel_info.description:
I'm Robbie Kramer 🎙Host of The Inner Confidence Podcast & Founder of Inner Confidence, Inc.

I lived an exhilarating single life filled with adventures and lessons, and ultimately achieved what I had always aspired to – finding an amazing, feminine, and loving wife. 

I believe my experiences provide a rare balance of wild freedom and committed love, equipping me with the insights to help you navigate the complexities of dating and relationships in today's world. Let me guide you to embrace your desires, improve your social prowess, and ultimately attract the partner who aligns with your highest aspirations.

You won’t find any fluffy, new-age, or cringy stuff here, just tested, proven and actionable advice that yields results.

Apply to join our exclusive Inner Confidence Community of ambitious men who are actively working together to achieve their goals faster   ► https://innerconfidence.com/community

You can email me at robbie@innerconfidence.com with any questions or comments.
